# Archive Agent Instructions

Read `AGENTS.md` first. It is the canonical instruction file for this
repository.

Important defaults:

- Active code lives in `AgentLens/` and `skills/`.
- Follow subtree `AGENTS.md` files before editing skill internals.
- Keep `.waygent/`, `.agentlens/`, `.claude/`, `.codex-orchestrator/`,
  `.orchestrator/`, `.superpowers/`, caches, build outputs, and secrets out of
  git.
- Verify changes with the smallest relevant command and report the command
  result.
